item.title: JXLL- Ruthless [Rap, Hip-hop]
item.dc:creator: therealejoc
item.description:
Decent project. If your looking to make a rap beat, don’t make the intro too long, his will turn people away from a rap song almost immediately. Also maybe change the instruments a little bit, might fit some darker sounding instruments better. If your like me you might just try lowpassing and reverbinfnit to give it a slacker vibe, or you could try something completely different. Good start
